data.description: ********************OFFER DEADLINE SUNDAY 2/18 AT 9AM******************** Country charm with modern flair and stunning views!  This meticulously updated home offers the perfect blend of rustic charm and modern style. The picturesque property is nestled on a sprawling 3 acre lot  overlooking a tranquil pond situated just across the street. The back yard is your private haven for outdoor living, featuring an expansive 1500+ square foot sidewalk and natural stone patio constructed in 2022 and a fire pit area perfect for entertaining. LVP flooring in the spacious living room greet you, and the updated kitchen with a large island and dining area (2020) will wow you. Wood stove in family room adds warmth and character, with updated mantel and insert. New LVP in enclosed porch and laundry/mud room.  Upstairs you will find 2 recently renovated full baths, and spacious bedrooms with original hardwood floors and ceiling fans.  Primary bedroom includes en-suite bath.  The basement features a newly finished rec room  and lots of room for storage. The home sits far back from the road, offering a long driveway leading to the two car garage and accessible shed adjacent to driveway. Additional updates include fresh paint (2020-2024), roof/gutters, French patio doors, interior doors, lighting/fans/electric in first floor, Andersen windows (2020), and appliances, water heater and softener and septic line/access (2017). Schedule your tour and let the beauty of this countryside escape capture your heart.
